<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - LibaraNHS</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Learn about LibaraNHS and our mission to automate NHS job applications">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50">
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

<section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center text-slate-800 mb-12">About LibaraNHS</h1>

        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="card mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    At LibaraNHS, we're dedicated to simplifying the NHS job application process for healthcare professionals across the UK. We understand that your time is valuable, and applying to multiple positions can be time-consuming and repetitive.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    We envision a future where healthcare professionals can focus entirely on their passion for patient care, while technology handles the administrative burden of job searching and applications.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Our Values</h2>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 text-lg">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
                        <span><strong>Efficiency:</strong> Save time and effort with automated processes</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
                        <span><strong>Security:</strong> Your data and credentials are encrypted and protected</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
                        <span><strong>Excellence:</strong> Deliver high-quality applications every time</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
                        <span><strong>Support:</strong> Dedicated customer service for all users</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>

<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
